{"id": "1441334737301147648", "channel_id": "1441334737301147648", "type": 0, "author_id": "428188931809607681", "author_name": "genericid.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Went from 8574 Health to 6393, but only 687 Damage is told to be taken. The \"Onyx Plume\" Damage was 189. Excluding the Onyx Plume, which applied corrosion and did not take it, The health is 8385 to 6393. The actual damage taken was 1992, and the damage which took corrosion advantage was 498(687-189). This shows that only exactly 1/4 of damage was calculated as being dealt, so that 300% damage from corrosion was left out.", "timestamp": "2025-11-21T07:49:40.077000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1441334737934483569", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 652790, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1441334737301147648/1441334737934483569/image.png?ex=69ff8fd4&is=69fe3e54&hm=fac0b6e67861b7028fccab34c7e25df852eb4c30951119fe77e424c9e57a1cd3&"}, {"id": "1441334738588798996", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 688192, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1441334737301147648/1441334738588798996/image.png?ex=69ff8fd4&is=69fe3e54&hm=f2ea0dfeb32b3f2303fc997ddc2b0bb37de494a065f05f416aa302d0fa972fe5&"}, {"id": "1441334739058298921", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 664706, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1441334737301147648/1441334739058298921/image.png?ex=69ff8fd4&is=69fe3e54&hm=6aae2c53233d1e793b5c213b447e0754f792d56a42f603c756573aa20af61f28&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1441334737301147648", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Corrosion Damage is not correctly included in 'Deal XX damage in one turn' calculation", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "13